I was born on the third of January, 1901. At - in Old Woodstock rather, at the Old Gatehouse, that's where my parents lived. I'm the eldest of four sons. About eighteen months between us all. Now what was the second thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid876133 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8269814\charrsid3017333 I want your full name.
